document_data.name: Ship Taerl
document_data.mainbody: '''Ship Taerl''' was one of the five factions of [[Luskan]] ruled by a [[High Captains (Luskan)|High Captain]]. It was named for and originally led by High Captain [[Taerl]].
document_data.Relationships: Ship Taerl was allied with [[Ship Baram]] in [[1376 DR]].
document_data.Members:
* [[Throa Taerl]], leader by [[1489 DR]]
* [[Taerl]], former leader
